05:33.032 --> 05:35.768
<i>People behave oddly
around the bereaved.</i>

05:35.769 --> 05:36.903
Hey.

05:36.904 --> 05:38.905
<i>They can't help themselves.</i>

05:38.906 --> 05:42.041
- I'm sorry.
