It must be so painful,

06:39.033 --> 06:42.268
so lonely.

06:43.170 --> 06:48.406
<i>She was wrong, of course. My parents
were gone, but I had my sister, Joan.</i>

06:49.809 --> 06:52.977
<i>And we didn't know
what trouble we were in.</i>

06:55.081 --> 06:58.651
So I have to ask, Dr. King. What's
the story with the clock there?

06:58.652 --> 07:00.386
