interview them all, yes?

08:00.548 --> 08:04.182
Most. Uh-huh. Yes.

08:05.818 --> 08:10.322
100,000 genes, several
thousand women,

08:10.323 --> 08:12.025
and no certain outcome?

08:12.026 --> 08:14.394
