well into our research.

08:14.395 --> 08:18.730
- Oh, well, how far along are you?
- Um...

08:22.735 --> 08:26.404
So, 74...

08:26.473 --> 08:29.642
No, no. Um...

08:29.643 --> 08:33.145
- six more.
- Uh-huh.

08:33.746 --> 08:36.313
So, 80...

08:38.885 --> 08:41.653
Um...

08:46.292 --> 08:50.297
Right. Well, thank you. Thank you so
much for your time and your hospitality.

08:50.298 --> 08:53.466
We'll... we'll be in touch. And
we're obviously very interested

08:53.467 --> 08:57.068
in helping you with something
so important, so...

09:05.344 --> 09:08.681
