charming in a way.

10:06.907 --> 10:09.408
- Did you tell him about the...
- No, I...

10:09.409 --> 10:12.044
- He wasn't having any of it.
- We could...

10:12.045 --> 10:14.546
Okay. I see.

10:15.048 --> 10:18.250
So, thank you...

10:18.752 --> 10:21.553
for coming out.

10:25.591 --> 10:29.562
