21:26.051 --> 21:28.186
I know.

21:28.588 --> 21:31.023
- I know.
- Come here.

21:31.024 --> 21:34.193
Come here. Come here.

21:34.194 --> 21:39.264
Well, at least she went quick.
Not like my wife.

21:39.265 --> 21:44.102
Boy, she took her time, didn't she?
I mean, it was endless suffering.

21:44.103 --> 21:46.237
Endless.

21:49.575 --> 21:51.977
My God.

21:51.978 --> 21:54.780
First your mother,

21:54.781 --> 21:57.649
then your father.

21:57.650 --> 22:01.685
Now... poor Joan.

22:13.665 --> 22:17.502
You again? Cool.

22:17.503 --> 22:21.039
